{"tid":88642,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本酒店問題","createTime":"2017-01-20T17:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T15:33:39.000Z","uid":5365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"196432744371e41bc351986583ad6310b397ed08","tid":88642,"uid":5365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T17:46:27.000Z","msg":"其實住左咁多次日本酒店有個問題我都拆解唔到<br />\n點樣可以將個冷氣搞到真係出冷風<br />\n冬天係日本住酒店個冷氣自動出暖風熱到仆街<br />\n搞到要開窗瞓<br />\n<br />\n有無手足識搞個冷氣？<br />\n次次都係Sanyo"},{"pid":"047fe60f3f16298a7079369d7b49985ce281435d","tid":88642,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T17:47:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實住左咁多次日本酒店有個問題我都拆解唔到<br />\n點樣可以將個冷氣搞到真係出冷風<br />\n冬天係日本住酒店個冷氣自動出暖風熱到仆街<br />\n搞到要開窗瞓<br />\n<br />\n有無手足識搞個冷氣？<br />\n次次都係Sanyo</blockquote><br />\n好似無<br />\n<br />\n利申兩次都住Apa，問Counter話冬天自動轉去暖房mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae4e1ab37d8579d3d892fe20986c532d53c9409c","tid":88642,"uid":5365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T17:58:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實住左咁多次日本酒店有個問題我都拆解唔到<br />\n點樣可以將個冷氣搞到真係出冷風<br />\n冬天係日本住酒店個冷氣自動出暖風熱到仆街<br />\n搞到要開窗瞓<br />\n<br />\n有無手足識搞個冷氣？<br />\n次次都係Sanyo</blockquote><br />\n好似無<br />\n<br />\n利申兩次都住Apa，問Counter話冬天自動轉去暖房mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n熱到仆街"},{"pid":"4b520caa7e476fb174decbcc8869fe2bbb24d44e","tid":88642,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T18:00:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實住左咁多次日本酒店有個問題我都拆解唔到<br />\n點樣可以將個冷氣搞到真係出冷風<br />\n冬天係日本住酒店個冷氣自動出暖風熱到仆街<br />\n搞到要開窗瞓<br />\n<br />\n有無手足識搞個冷氣？<br />\n次次都係Sanyo</blockquote><br />\n好似無<br />\n<br />\n利申兩次都住Apa，問Counter話冬天自動轉去暖房mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n熱到仆街</blockquote><br />\n日本好多酒店設計到個窗可以開到好大作為逃生門之用，你試吓開大個窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19862e53b90609b0dbff8f49b859da34a12e2a8b","tid":88642,"uid":38351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T21:27:08.000Z","msg":"同感<br />\n有次住間旅館見有remote 即衝去開冷氣，點知唔得，係都出暖風<br />\n之後，員工上門攞野俾我時問職員點較冷風。佢講法同樓上一樣，無得較，旅館set 死咗。<br />\n之後想開窗，但旅館鎖死咗。職員再call 上司上嚟親自開<br />\n講咁大段野，想講開唔到窗未必單單安全鎖，可能係要call 職員開鎖"},{"pid":"08ae9dfb37400370e94a295fde3c053c20065582","tid":88642,"uid":19301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T03:04:37.000Z","msg":"APA 應該無得自己較<br />\n佢中央控制"},{"pid":"b5da84f285fecae46548a62dd368e066c371cac0","tid":88642,"uid":5365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T05:44:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>APA 應該無得自己較<br />\n佢中央控制</blockquote><br />\n相信連鎖都係用Sanyo<br />\n住過幾間都係咁<br />\n<br />\n熱過夏天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b57c4a1beeb823ec88af367aede5728fe388651d","tid":88642,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:38:31.000Z","msg":"Dormy inn反而有得較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1caca6333f32db6f709ea43dcf529313bfe95a90","tid":88642,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T07:08:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Dormy inn反而有得較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n網走果間教唔到，不過有窗開"},{"pid":"ccd69dbe134c6549f12381cf645772983f3347a4","tid":88642,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T07:13:28.000Z","msg":"我都試過酒店中央暖氣熱到出晒汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果好彩開到窗，如果唔係真係唔知點算<br />\n<br />\n都幾怕冬天去日本，唔知應該著幾多衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 著得多一入室內又熱得濟，著得唔夠室外就凍到pk<br />\n佢地室內d暖氣開到好似唔洗錢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\